    {
      "id": "1ab4750c-f3ba-8017-903a-fdcc402822b0",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Students often struggle with writing tasks due to having underdeveloped SRL skills. Authors do an experiment on 44 undergraduate students. They collect trace data from multiple channels and investigate how behavior influences essay score.  Findings show that  metacognitive monitoring benefits writing quality. ",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
        "id": "1ab4750c-f3ba-8017-903a-fdcc402822b0",
